  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist the full game right here...</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><i>NAIRI: Rising Tide - Prologue</i> is a free playable demo of <i>NAIRI: Rising Tide</i>, the second chapter in the exciting graphic adventure series <i>NAIRI</i>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/e1365a7c03709f133b44e6b18ff2816a.poster.avif?t=1740505593\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/e1365a7c03709f133b44e6b18ff2816a.webm?t=1740505593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/e1365a7c03709f133b44e6b18ff2816a.mp4?t=1740505593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In <i>NAIRI: Rising Tide</i>, Nairi continues on a  perilous quest to save her family.<br>As she and her companions try to overcome the many dangers of the corrupt city of Shirin, an apocalyptic prophecy threatens to devour everything...<br><br>This free version contains around 20 minutes of gameplay and sets the scene for what will be an exciting second chapter!<br><br>If you’ve not yet explored <i>NAIRI: Tower of Shirin</i> it’s available right now! <br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/91c9fd2326a026aa521f193ae178be5d.poster.avif?t=1740505593\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/91c9fd2326a026aa521f193ae178be5d.webm?t=1740505593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/91c9fd2326a026aa521f193ae178be5d.mp4?t=1740505593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>NAIRI: Rising Tide - Prologue</i> is a free playable demo of <i>NAIRI: Rising Tide</i>, the second chapter in the exciting graphic adventure series <i>NAIRI</i>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/e1365a7c03709f133b44e6b18ff2816a.poster.avif?t=1740505593\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/e1365a7c03709f133b44e6b18ff2816a.webm?t=1740505593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/e1365a7c03709f133b44e6b18ff2816a.mp4?t=1740505593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In <i>NAIRI: Rising Tide</i>, Nairi continues on a  perilous quest to save her family.<br>As she and her companions try to overcome the many dangers of the corrupt city of Shirin, an apocalyptic prophecy threatens to devour everything...<br><br>This free version contains around 20 minutes of gameplay and sets the scene for what will be an exciting second chapter!<br><br>If you’ve not yet explored <i>NAIRI: Tower of Shirin</i> it’s available right now! <br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/91c9fd2326a026aa521f193ae178be5d.poster.avif?t=1740505593\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/91c9fd2326a026aa521f193ae178be5d.webm?t=1740505593\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1225060/extras/91c9fd2326a026aa521f193ae178be5d.mp4?t=1740505593\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>",
